reviews.text:
I used TFA Coconut Extra at half the percentage, and this stuff is extraordinary!  Very well balanced pineapple kick with a little coconut and best of all, it doesn't taste like suntan lotion! (Although the smell is reminiscent in a very good way)&#xD;
&#xD;
I will definitely make this one again, and I'm glad I got 30s of INW Pineapple and FA Coconut.  If you don't have FA Coconut, get plenty.  It's a decently versatile ingredient that can be used in many popular recipes.
